item.title: About
item.description: This site The goal is to consolidate the content that I have published on my Youtube channel, RPubs, Github, my company’s website, as well as non-confidential material from on my own work. The main purpose is to have an archive ready as a personal reference, i.e. myself looking things up. Maybe it also helps others. Me My name is Martin Geissmann. I studied economics in Basel and Zurich before my professional track led me to healthcare management.
